                &lt;span class=&quot;comment-copy&quot;&gt;I have never seen the notation &lt;code&gt;T (&amp;amp;)[SIZE]&lt;/code&gt;. Can you explain what this means? Also you could mention constexpr in this context.&lt;/span&gt;

