            &lt;/div&gt;

            &lt;div class=&quot;comment-body js-comment-edit-hide&quot;&gt;

                &lt;span class=&quot;comment-copy&quot;&gt;That&apos;s nice if you use c++ and you actually have a variable of an array type. Neither of them is the case in the question: Language is C, and the thing the OP wants to get the array size from is a simple pointer.&lt;/span&gt;

