            &lt;div class=&quot;comment-body js-comment-edit-hide&quot;&gt;

                &lt;span class=&quot;comment-copy&quot;&gt;Your code is full of comments, but I think it would make everything easier if you added some general explanation of how this works outside of code, as normal text. Can you please &lt;a href=&quot;https://stackoverflow.com/posts/42734883/edit&quot;&gt;edit&lt;/a&gt; your question and do it? Thank you!&lt;/span&gt;

